==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wheel of fortune
<hw>Wheel of fortune</hw>. <def>A gambling or lottery device consisting
of a wheel which is spun horizontally, articles or sums to which certain
marks on its circumference point when it stops being distributed
according to varying rules.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wheel-shaped</ent>⟦br⟧
